OL,3,CWhat are the key takeaways from the
OL,4,Cnew transgender guidance for schools?
OL,6,FThe Department for Education (DfE) has
OL,7,Fpublished its long-awaited draft
OL,8,Fguidance for schools and colleges on
OL,9,Fhow best to support pupils questioning
OL,10,Ftheir gender, after it was delayed
OL,11,Ffrom the summer.
OL,13,FThe non-statutory guidance says
OL,14,F"parents should not be excluded" from
OL,15,Fdecisions taken by a school or college
OL,16,Frelating to requests for a child to
OL,17,F"socially transition", such as wishes
OL,18,Fto change names, pronouns and clothing.
